# Marketing Guidelines

## SEO Strategy
### Primary Keywords
- "construction company Port Elizabeth"
- "building contractors Eastern Cape"
- "residential construction Port Elizabeth"
- "commercial building contractors"

### Local SEO
- Optimize for "Port Elizabeth construction services"
- Include Eastern Cape region mentions
- Local business schema markup
- Google My Business optimization

## Content Marketing
### Blog Topics
- Construction industry trends in South Africa
- Home building tips for Eastern Cape climate
- Project management best practices
- Client success stories and case studies

### Social Media Strategy
- Share project progress photos
- Post client testimonials
- Construction tips and insights
- Local community involvement
